<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;div class="tag"&gt;AI Texting Assistant&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;h1&gt;Stop&lt;br&gt;overthinking&lt;br&gt;texts.&lt;/h1&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;p class="subtitle"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>SheTexted analyzes your chat and tells you exactly what to reply — confident, natural, and matched to the vibe.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;a class="cta" href="https://t.me/SheTextedBot" target="_blank"&gt;Open Telegram Bot&lt;/a&gt;</p>
